g.text: "US1002 - Register a job opening" Sequence Diagram
asks to register a job opening
Shows company list and asks to select one
Requests typed data (Number of Vacancies and Job Function)
Shows Mode list (remote, hybrid, onsite...) and asks to select one
Shows Contract Types list (full-time, part-time,...) and asks to select one
Requests typed data( Address (street, city, state, country, zip-code), Description)
display operation success and the data of the Job Opening created
